    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n             Post To Be - Omarion Ft. Chris Brown & Jhene Aiko\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTabbed by: \r\nE-mail: \r\n\r\nTuning: Standard (E,A,D,G)\r\n\r\nThis is the whole song. Simple, but rather catchy. Just listen to it to figure out the timing.\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-----------------------------3----44---------------------------------------|\r\nE|---2----4----66----4----4---------------2----------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| \\  slide down\r\n| h  hammer-on\r\n| p  pull-off\r\n| ~  vibrato\r\n| +  harmonic\r\n| x  Mute note\r\n===============================================================================",
